  <content>Example:

##{{{{{kanbancard document="Ideas.Idea1" title="title" columns="status,assignement" /}}}}}##

* ##document## [mandatory] is the document name to display
* ##title## title to use
* ##columns## additional columns to display
* ##cssClasses## cssClasses to use (default col-xs-12)

== Cards ==

(% class="row" %)
(((
(% class="col-sm-4" %)
(((
{{kanbancard document="Ideas.Idea1" title="title" columns="status,assignement" cssStyles="margin: 4px;"/}}
)))
